{"tid":762961,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[分享] 大家既串生字心德","createTime":"2018-07-31T17:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T04:25:57.000Z","uid":170716,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"deceb27cbacb64a205d4878ea9232df662f6dff5","tid":762961,"uid":170716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:01:19.000Z","msg":"小弟當拿DSE英文得4 <br />\n自問語文能力差<br />\n加上係小毒男平時唔多同人溝通<br />\n但唔叻唔代表無興趣<br />\n畢業左之後繼續進修<br />\n得閒坐車會串下生字 睇下書咁<br />\n但好似好多時候都會覺得自己方法用錯 學得無效率<br />\n<br />\n我平時會一邊睇書一邊查字典<br />\n查完寫落本notebook到<br />\n有時覺得佢寫得好會抄低成句<br />\n得閒會拎本野出黎溫下咁<br />\n<br />\n睇動畫 電影都係一樣會寫低d字之後溫<br />\n但好似串極都仲有<br />\n沒完沒了<br />\n同時自己又成日唔記得D字<br />\n<br />\n由於抄落黎d字真係愈黎愈多<br />\n去到一個無從入手既地步<br />\n未溫完之前幾頁又多左幾十頁新既等住查<br />\n多到唔知點重溫D舊生字<br />\n<br />\n有無高手分享下心德<br />\n(唔好同我講串生字無用呢D廢話)"},{"pid":"06e16a52422837744540cc1c8960e456e65cdff7","tid":762961,"uid":45872,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:15:46.000Z","msg":"試下用拼音串字 九成字都可以拼出嚟唔使死記<br />\n利伸由細到大都唔會特登背生字 大部分都係拼出嚟"},{"pid":"24999cfbc49706152efa934d0e953db56987c2a6","tid":762961,"uid":140580,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:31:16.000Z","msg":"心得吖<br />\n<br />\n入正題：試下將啲字分類黎記"},{"pid":"d73a9cb3bb42b36c2222196452a641de880bfd11","tid":762961,"uid":12000,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"學好自己母語先"},{"pid":"9e3a2c90e0cd62aa9ead7b401db40e1bde5c6dbd","tid":762961,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06e16a52422837744540cc1c8960e456e65cdff7","tid":762961,"uid":45872,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:15:46.000Z","msg":"試下用拼音串字 九成字都可以拼出嚟唔使死記<br />\n利伸由細到大都唔會特登背生字 大部分都係拼出嚟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:38:57.000Z","msg":"我用呢個方法都好有效"},{"pid":"a6d478e552d2aeb098c0085275013c2a6fb0584d","tid":762961,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:40:25.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得啲字識讀就會識串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84de34c8511311e0d98f00c32e171c3506ce6811","tid":762961,"uid":170716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d73a9cb3bb42b36c2222196452a641de880bfd11","tid":762961,"uid":12000,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:32:41.000Z","msg":"學好自己母語先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:00:37.000Z","msg":"興趣黎 無分主次"},{"pid":"c141ee4800f00ca66fc801938caa749a55a26ee2","tid":762961,"uid":170716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6d478e552d2aeb098c0085275013c2a6fb0584d","tid":762961,"uid":90820,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:40:25.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得啲字識讀就會識串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:11:47.000Z","msg":"但有時係成隻字唔記得左<br />\n唔似中文可以用object後推斷番個字<br />\n中文字每隻字都係symbols<br />\n而英文alphabets自己本身無意思<br />\nSignifier 同 signified 無關連<br />\n所以唔記得左就唔記得左"},{"pid":"b7a8224447d01f42bab2a972717ecc439a809567","tid":762961,"uid":170716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24999cfbc49706152efa934d0e953db56987c2a6","tid":762961,"uid":140580,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T17:31:16.000Z","msg":"心得吖<br />\n<br />\n入正題：試下將啲字分類黎記"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T18:13:53.000Z","msg":"中文文盲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點樣分類？"},{"pid":"47e7b62cfa9b48b63c2210d797d59c9911ab7c13","tid":762961,"uid":140580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T10:27:24.000Z","msg":"跟verb noun adjective分又得<br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得最好就跟主題或者範疇<br />\ne.g. 科學 地理 social issues吖咁<br />\n<br />\n即係好似小學生咁<br />\nSpring summer autumn winter <br />\nExciting boring interesting touching <br />\n都會group埋一齊學"},{"pid":"e0481348b9739428e9830b158fe371e02e9a1f0b","tid":762961,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c141ee4800f00ca66fc801938caa749a55a26ee2","tid":762961,